{"tid":2354205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾國衞：個人認為區議員屬公職人員 正研修例是否包括區議員宣誓","createTime":"2021-01-05T09:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T00:50:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d324c2a28e7189c89f94c7ab6cad41e263c6a794","tid":2354205,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局長曾國衞在立法會政制事務委員會上表示，當局正研究就全國人大常委會對《基本法》第104條的解釋，修訂本地法例。至於會否包含區議員的宣誓安排，他指，第104條並無包括區議員，但《港區國安法》第6條就規定，香港居民參選及就任公職時，要簽署文件或宣誓，確認擁護《基本法》及效忠香港特區，當中並無明確定義公職人員，他個人認為區議員應包括在內，政府正檢視如何作出明確界定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2373528&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGxVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=f05b4c46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373528</a>"},{"pid":"1a9c022ef7b58279afa52a31d4e13276bf99f1ad","tid":2354205,"uid":76753,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:49:26.000Z","msg":"個人認為"},{"pid":"5b34f5a16dbca41a61b6fbb2beaf13d6d93df504","tid":2354205,"uid":111253,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:49:56.000Z","msg":"個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 索性話黨認為啦"},{"pid":"aad38ff48f38a7d0440f269238f2d44b1ed71a57","tid":2354205,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"2019年尾當選，2020年中立惡法，清朝劍斬宋朝官，落地獄呀狗官"},{"pid":"1eefe66d2b79efdfa33badd86e03c61613b816ec","tid":2354205,"uid":33028,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:52:42.000Z","msg":"其實而家參選區議會都要簽文件保證效忠特區"},{"pid":"c854d1ea28dbb4238acb41bf5751e5c29f32fb18","tid":2354205,"uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"簽咪簽，立法會議員一開始夠宣誓，都冇用嘅<br />\n做吓樣咪算"},{"pid":"96a38541b8294855522f574483fa03bb128a83a2","tid":2354205,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit